{"tid":1886683,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"免費A酸比有需要人士","createTime":"2020-02-19T05:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T13:47:44.000Z","uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"528430402753844c836baa7a9a402f733c98c31d","tid":1886683,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:16:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我喺網上買咗180(<span style=\"color: gold;\">20mg</span>)粒A酸 (一日吃一粒)<br />\n但係有60粒會喺我食完之前過期<br />\n嗰60粒會喺5月1之後號過期<br />\n<br />\n但係好好彩<br />\n嗰間嘢肯免費畀返60粒我<br />\n<br />\n所以會過期嗰60粒如果我唔食嘅話就要揼<br />\n吃A酸睇醫生都唔平<br />\n我唔想嘥咗個60粒A酸<br />\n如果你有需要嘅話可以搵我TG: abcrfc132<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我只會收返你20蚊車馬費</span>"},{"pid":"94d529444ae16bef157ee40ffeadc937d83940c7","tid":1886683,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FsDNPmT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFsDNPmT.jpg&h=99f4bb34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afa8d8a49cc80a5f1bb19eeb6171132a1ce9587a","tid":1886683,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"有冇免費vyvanse"},{"pid":"e63075029b646335087f3d611e80b225a2a91622","tid":1886683,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"已有人要左 用再問"},{"pid":"e9d1a8ecc56cbf60f3674e74b7d653e93a8c7279","tid":1886683,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T21:12:59.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n食到肝衰竭<br />\n咪害人啦"},{"pid":"f04ba54ac45467c3087edf0998cb3efa274938e0","tid":1886683,"uid":322230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9d1a8ecc56cbf60f3674e74b7d653e93a8c7279","tid":1886683,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T21:12:59.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n食到肝衰竭<br />\n咪害人啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"你讀醫?"},{"pid":"9b1a7c62e2337a159fe82071adab4f3383e16a04